  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0baf\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Denying the genocide is the final step in the genocide - Ontario MP Vijay",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The ultimate step in genocide is to deny that a genocide took place. So we will continue to share stories related to the Tamilnadu massacre.",
        "Vijay Thanikachalam, Member of Parliament for the Province of Ontario, Canada, said that through awareness and discussion on the genocide in Sri Lanka and around the world, we can prevent such incidents in the future and help our community recover from this tragedy.",
        "The Ontario High Court last Tuesday dismissed a petition filed by some organizations, including the Sri Lanka-Canadian Action Coalition, challenging Bill 104 of the Tamil Genocide Awareness Weekly submitted to the Ontario Provincial Parliament of Canada.",
        "In this context, Ontario Provincial Councilor Vijay Thanikachalam has stated in a statement issued in connection with the judgment of the Ontario High Court.",
        "A petition challenging the Tamil Genocide Awareness Week Act has been dismissed by the High Court and has been accepted as constitutional.",
        "More than 60 Tamil organizations submitted submissions to the court in support of the bill.",
        "In particular, the judge in this case pointed out that 'by informing the public about the Tamil massacre and other massacres, such violence and abuses can be avoided in the future'.",
        "We know from past histories that denying that a genocide took place is the final step in genocide. So we will continue to share stories related to the Tamilnadu massacre.",
        "We will inform others about what happened to the Tamils. He said that through awareness and discussion on the genocide in Sri Lanka and globally, such incidents could be avoided in the future and our community could contribute to the recovery from this tragedy."
      ],
